Package com.company.parserUtil

Class EntryParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.parserUtil.EntryParser
  • public class EntryParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for parsing an entry (record) that is in String

    This class provided a few static method, including factory that return a new Entry and methods for getting information about entry such as: type, key etc.
